[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0436","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0436.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0251","title":"Unix Talkd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Talkd（talk守护进程）存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制请求，破坏目标用户的终端显示内容，导致正常会话中断或系统服务异常。该漏洞影响早期Unix/Linux系统中运行的talk服务，攻击者可通过网络连接利用该缺陷进行远程拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0251"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.253","remediation":"立即禁用 talkd 服务（`systemctl disable talkd --now` 或 `killall talkd`），并在防火墙层面拦截 UDP/TCP 517 端口（`iptables -A INPUT -p udp --dport 517 -j DROP`）。如业务需要使用 talk 服务，应升级操作系统的 talkd 实现至修复版本或迁移至加密替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0251","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0251.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0251.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0251","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0251.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0251.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4pmp-8rgh-2hrv/GHSA-4pmp-8rgh-2hrv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0251.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82087/info.html","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0251.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0436.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0434","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0434.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0249","title":"Microsoft Windows NT RSHSVC 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 系统中的 RSHSVC（远程 Shell 服务）存在远程代码执行漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该服务缺乏足够访问控制的问题，通过网络连接向目标系统的 RSHSVC 端口发送特制请求，从而以系统权限执行任意命令，实现完全控制目标主机。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 版本，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0249"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.987","remediation":"Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 均已生命周期结束，建议立即升级到受支持版本的 Windows（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）以彻底消除该漏洞。如无法升级，可采取缓解措施：通过服务管理器停止 RSHSVC 服务并将启动类型设为\"禁用\"；同时在防火墙层面阻止外部对 TCP 514 等 rsh 相关端口的访问，限制仅授权管理 IP 可访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0249","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0249.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0249.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0249","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0249.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0249.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0249.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0249.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0434.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0421","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0421.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0236","title":"NCSA HTTPd / Apache httpd ScriptAlias 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"NCSA 1.3/1.4.x/1.5 及 Apache HTTPd 0.8.11/0.8.14 的 ScriptAlias 目录配置存在源码泄露漏洞。攻击者可通过直接访问 ScriptAlias 指定目录下的 CGI 程序文件，绕过服务器对脚本的正常执行处理，从而以明文方式读取 CGI 程序的源代码，导致数据库连接凭证、业务逻辑及内部算法等敏感信息暴露。远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用此漏洞，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0236"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.393","remediation":"立即升级至 Apache HTTPD 2.4.x 或更新版本（NCSA httpd 已停止维护超过 20 年），该漏洞已在 Apache 1.x 后续版本修复。确保 ScriptAlias 目录配置中不包含源文件读取权限，移除不必要的目录映射并限制 CGI 目录的访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0236","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20595","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0236.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0236.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0236","https://github.com/kenhuangus/llm-wiki/blob/d2bd485921f6c7b6071afbb389f44ab8e4e83c69/wiki/security/cve/cve-1999-0236.md","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/httpd/CVE-1999-0236.nopatch","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0236.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xgp2-4cpq-g2m7/GHSA-xgp2-4cpq-g2m7.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0236.yaml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0236.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0421.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0421.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0421.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0389","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0389.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0204","title":"Sendmail 8.6.9 ident 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.6.9 在处理 IDENT 协议查询时存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证，可通过向目标邮件服务器发送特制的 IDENT 请求触发该漏洞，以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Sendmail 8.6.9 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议升级至最新版本的 Sendmail 以修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0204"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:54.363","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本以彻底修复 IDENT 协议处理缺陷；编辑 sendmail.cf 配置文件，将 timeout.ident 设置为 0 以禁用 IDENT 查询功能；若暂时无法升级，在边界防火墙上拦截入站 TCP 端口 113（IDENT 服务端口）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0204","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20599","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-0204.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0204.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0204","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0204.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0204.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/669.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0204.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3rcf-hxhh-73gh/GHSA-3rcf-hxhh-73gh.json","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/667.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/sendmail_ident.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0389.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0387","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0387.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0202","title":"WU wu-ftpd 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd 中的 tar 命令在处理特制的文件名时存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过 FTP 会话上传包含恶意文件名的 tar 归档文件，当服务器端自动调用 tar 命令处理时，嵌入在文件名中的任意命令将被执行，导致攻击者获得服务器完整控制权。此漏洞影响 wu-ftpd 2.4 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0202"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:54.110","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.6.0 或更高版本；若无法升级，在 ftpaccess 配置文件中禁用 tar 命令执行权限（\"tar /bin/tarn\" 注释掉）；建议迁移至 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD 等仍在维护的 FTP 服务器软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0202"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0387.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0385","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0385.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0201","title":"FTP服务器 quote cwd 命令路径信息泄露漏洞","description":"FTP 服务器的 `quote cwd` 命令存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送特制的 `CWD` 命令，使服务器返回 `ftp` 用户主目录的完整路径。该漏洞可被用于收集目标系统的目录结构信息，为后续攻击提供侦察支撑。影响多种 FTP 服务器软件，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0201"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.990","remediation":"升级 FTP 服务器软件至最新版本（如 vsftpd 3.0.5+、ProFTPD 1.3.8+），并在配置文件中启用 chroot 功能（如 vsftpd 设置 chroot_local_user=YES），将 ftp 用户限制在其主目录内，防止路径泄露。如无法升级，在 ftp 用户主目录下创建空的 .bashrc 文件可缓解部分信息暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0201"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0385.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0359","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0359.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0179","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 3.51 Samba 共享目录遍历拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95 和 Windows NT 3.51 系统中的 Samba 文件共享服务存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过客户端连接到目标系统的 Samba 共享目录后，执行 \"cd ..\" 命令，导致系统崩溃或死锁，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 及 NT 3.51 版本，危害等级中危，利用条件低、无需身份认证。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0179"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.160","remediation":"微软已停止支持 Windows 95 和 Windows NT 3.51，建议立即升级至受支持的操作系统版本（如 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2019+）。如无法升级，可在 Samba 服务端配置文件 smb.conf 中设置 veto files = /..*/ 禁止访问上级目录，或在防火墙层面限制 SMB 端口（TCP 139/445）仅对可信来源开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ140818"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0359.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0354","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0354.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0178","title":"O'Reilly WebSite 服务器 win-c-sample.exe 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"O'Reilly WebSite Web 服务器 1.1e 及之前版本中自带的 win-c-sample.exe 示例程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向该程序发送超长查询字符串（query string）触发栈缓冲区溢出，从而在服务器进程中执行任意代码。该漏洞无需身份认证，攻击复杂度较低，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。受影响版本包括 OReilly WebSite 1.x 至 2.0 系列。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0178"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.037","remediation":"删除 WebSite 安装目录下的 win-c-sample.exe 文件即可消除此漏洞。该文件为调试示例程序，删除不影响 Web 服务器正常功能。若需长期解决方案，建议迁移至仍在维护中的 Web 服务器软件（如 Apache httpd、Nginx 或 IIS），并避免在生产环境部署包含示例/调试文件的任何软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1997_1/0021.html","http://www.osvdb.org/8","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2078","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/295","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20484","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0178.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0178","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0178.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0178.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0178.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-339v-jgw2-82mh/GHSA-339v-jgw2-82mh.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/WebSite.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0354.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0344","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0344.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0173","title":"Matt Wright FormMail 1.x 跨站请求伪造漏洞","description":"Matt Wright FormMail 1.x CGI 程序存在跨站请求伪造漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意表单提交请求，利用目标服务器上的 FormMail 脚本发送匿名邮件。由于程序未对来源服务器进行合法性校验，任何可访问该 CGI 的第三方均可滥用其邮件转发功能，导致垃圾邮件发送或敏感信息泄露。攻击者无需身份认证，只需诱骗用户访问恶意链接即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0173"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.420","remediation":"升级到 FormMail 2.0 或更高版本，该版本原生支持 @referers 域名白名单校验机制。如无法升级，手动编辑 formmail.pl，设置 @referers 数组为仅允许的域名列表（如 @referers = ('example.com')），并移除脚本中未授权的邮件发送功能。此外，在 Web 服务器层面限制该 CGI 脚本仅允许特定 Host 头来源访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0173","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20486","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0173.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0173","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0173.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0173.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0173.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw47-w8q9-cxg3/GHSA-jw47-w8q9-cxg3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0173.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0344.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0344.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0344.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0342","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0342.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0171","title":"Linux Kernel syslog 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 syslog 子系统存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者通过向目标系统发送大量冗余日志消息，可导致 syslog 服务因消息队列过载而无法正常处理其他进程日志，最终造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本，攻击门槛低，无需身份认证即可远程触发。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0171"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.180","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.x 或更高版本即可修复此漏洞。如在旧系统上无法升级，可替换 syslogd 为 rsyslog 或 syslog-ng，并启用速率限制（如 rsyslog 的 $SystemLogRateLimitInterval 指令），限制单来源每秒日志条数以缓解日志洪水 DoS。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0171"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0342.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0341","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0341.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0170","title":"DEC Ultrix NFS 挂载访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"Ultrix 和 OSF 操作系统中 NFS 服务存在访问控制绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可通过发送特制 NFS 挂载请求，绕过访问列表（export list）的限制，成功挂载本应被拒绝共享的远程文件系统，导致敏感数据未授权泄露。该漏洞源于 NFS 访问控制列表验证机制缺陷，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0170"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.047","remediation":"升级 Ultrix/OSF 至厂商已修复的最新版本，或安装 DEC 提供的安全补丁。在 `/etc/exports` 中严格限制可访问 NFS 共享的主机列表，使用 `-access=` 选项精确控制客户端 IP。在网络层面，通过防火墙阻断外部对 NFS 端口（TCP/UDP 2049、portmapper 111）的访问，仅允许受信任的内网主机。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0170"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0341.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0337","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0337.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0166","title":"NFS 导出的文件系统目录遍历漏洞","description":"NFS（网络文件系统）存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的NFS共享目录发送特制的\"cd ..\"路径跳转请求，绕过文件系统导出限制，访问导出目录之外的其他任意目录及文件。该漏洞影响多种Unix/Linux系统上的NFS服务，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，造成敏感信息泄露。CVSS评分5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0166"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:44.540","remediation":"升级 NFS 服务端至 NFSv3/v4 版本（如 Linux 内核 2.6+ 自带 nfsd），并检查 /etc/exports 配置文件，确保为每个导出目录显式设置 `fsid=0` 或 `fsid=UUID` 以建立正确的根文件系统边界；同时启用 `root_squash` 选项将远程 root 用户映射为匿名用户，避免提权；启用 `no_subtree_check` 选项减少因子树检查导致的权限绕过；最后在防火墙层面限制仅允许可信网段访问 2049/TCP 和 2049/UDP 端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0166"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0337.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0334","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0334.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0163","title":"Sendmail 管道字符命令注入漏洞","description":"Sendmail 存在命令注入漏洞，攻击者可通过在邮件地址或邮件头中插入管道符（|）构造恶意载荷，绕过安全检查执行任意系统命令，从而以 root 权限完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响早期版本 Sendmail，攻击无需身份认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0163"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:44.160","remediation":"升级 sendmail 至 8.8.3 或更高版本（该版本新增了 shell 元字符转义机制，阻止管道符注入攻击）。如无法升级，可采取以下缓解措施：1）限制 ~/.forward 文件仅允许受信任用户创建；2）确保 aliases 文件属主为 root 且权限为 644，禁止普通用户写入；3）在 sendmail.cf 中启用 `O DontBlameSendmail=forwardfileinsecure` 警告并监控异常 .forward 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0163"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0334.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0231","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0231.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0100","title":"IBM AIX innd 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 系统上的 INN（InterNetNews）新闻服务器 1.5.1 版本存在远程命令执行漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 innd 守护进程发送特制的控制消息（control messages），利用其处理逻辑缺陷执行任意命令，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 平台的 INN 1.5.1，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0100"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.217","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.0 及以上版本（当前最新为 2.7.x），旧版 innd 1.x 通过新闻组控制消息可远程执行命令，新版本已修复该问题。如无法升级，在 inn.conf 中将 `verify-cancel` 和 `verify-ihave` 设为 `always` 并限制 trusted peers 来源 IP 范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0100"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0231.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0445","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0445.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0260","title":"多款Web服务器 jj CGI程序 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"jj CGI 程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向该 CGI 程序传递包含 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）的特制请求参数，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响早期运行 jj CGI 程序的 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议禁用或移除受影响的 jj CGI 脚本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0260"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-12-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.353","remediation":"立即删除 jj CGI 脚本（通常位于 /cgi-bin/jj 路径），该脚本已过时且不适用于现代 Web 服务环境。如因兼容性必须使用，请在 Web 服务器配置中限制 CGI 执行权限并启用输入过滤，但最安全的做法是完全移除该 CGI 程序。同时审查服务器上其他 CGI 脚本是否存在类似 shell 元字符注入问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0260","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0260.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0260","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0260.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0260.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0260.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vqmv-6xp5-qh75/GHSA-vqmv-6xp5-qh75.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/J/jj.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.1183"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0445.toml"}]